properties.stmtText:
SUB-2000-PROCESS .
 
MOVE 0 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE LOW-VALUES TO FAKER-INFO-OCCS IN L-PARAMETER

SUB-9010-COMPANY .
 
MOVE 'FORMATS-COMPANY' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-FORMAT-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF FORMATS-COMPANY

ADD 1 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
SET FI-DX TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE W-TABLE-1 TO FAKER-TABLE IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )

MOVE W-FAKER-FORMAT TO W-RECURSED-FORMAT
MOVE 1 TO W-SUB-1
PERFORM SUB-2110-RECURSE-FORMATS THRU SUB-2110-EXIT UNTIL W-SUB-1 > LENGTH OF W-RECURSED-FORMAT OR NOT FAKER-RESPONSE-GOOD IN L-PARAMETER

MOVE SPACES TO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE 1 TO W-SUB-1 W-SUB-2
PERFORM SUB-2120-PROCESS-FORMATS THRU SUB-2120-EXIT UNTIL W-SUB-1 > LENGTH OF W-RECURSED-FORMAT OR W-SUB-2 > LENGTH OF FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER OR W-RECURSED-FORMAT ( W-SUB-1 : ) = SPACES

ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1
UNSTRING W-RECURSED-FORMAT DELIMITED W-FORMAT-END INTO W-FORMAT-ENTRY POINTER W-SUB-1
STRING W-FAKER-RESULT DELIMITED '  ' INTO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER POINTER W-SUB-2

SUB-9020-SUFFIX .
 
MOVE 'COMPANY-SUFFIXES' TO W-TABLE-1
SET ADDRESS OF L-COMPANY-TABLE-1 TO ADDRESS OF COMPANY-SUFFIXES

ADD 1 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
SET FI-DX TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE W-TABLE-1 TO FAKER-TABLE IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )

MOVE W-RANDOM-NO TO FAKER-RANDOM-NO-SUB IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE 0 TO W-FOUND-DX
PERFORM SUB-9710-FIND-FORMAT THRU SUB-9710-EXIT VARYING L-F-DX-1 FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL W-FOUND-DX > 0 OR L-F-DX-1 > L-FORMAT-ENTRY-CNT-1

ADD 1 TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
SET FI-DX TO FAKER-INFO-CNT IN L-PARAMETER
MOVE W-TABLE-2 TO FAKER-TABLE IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE W-RANDOM-NO TO FAKER-RANDOM-NO-SUB IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE 0 TO W-FOUND-DX
PERFORM SUB-9720-FIND-FORMAT THRU SUB-9720-EXIT VARYING L-F-DX-2 FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL W-FOUND-DX > 0 OR L-F-DX-2 > L-FORMAT-ENTRY-CNT-2
MOVE 'Random format not found' TO W-FAKER-FORMAT

SET W-FOUND-DX TO L-F-DX-2
MOVE W-FOUND-DX TO FAKER-TABLE-ENTRY IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE 'Random format not found' TO W-FAKER-FORMAT

SET W-FOUND-DX TO L-F-DX-1
MOVE W-FOUND-DX TO FAKER-TABLE-ENTRY IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )

COMPUTE W-RANDOM-SUB = FAKRAND-RANDOM-NO * L-COMPANY-ENTRY-CNT-1 + 1
MOVE W-RANDOM-SUB TO FAKER-RANDOM-NO-SUB IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX ) W-FOUND-DX FAKER-TABLE-ENTRY IN L-PARAMETER ( FI-DX )
MOVE L-COMPANY-ENTRY-1 ( W-FOUND-DX ) TO W-FAKER-RESULT
MOVE W-FAKER-RESULT TO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER

STRING W-FAKER-FORMAT DELIMITED '  ' INTO W-RECURSED-FORMAT POINTER W-SUB-1-SAVE
MOVE W-RECURSED-FORMAT-REST TO W-RECURSED-FORMAT ( W-SUB-1-SAVE : )
MOVE FAKER-RESULT IN W-FAKER-PARAMETER TO W-FAKER-RESULT

SUB-9200-LAST-NAME .
 
MOVE 'LAST-NAME' TO W-TABLE-1
SET PERSON-LAST-NAME IN W-FAKER-PARAMETER TO TRUE
CALL W-FAKPERS-PROG USING W-FAKER-PARAMETER

MOVE SPACES TO W-TABLE-1
SET FAKER-UNKNOWN-FORMAT IN L-PARAMETER TO TRUE
STRING 'Unknown FAKCOMP format "' W-FORMAT-ENTRY '"' DELIMITED SIZE INTO FAKER-RESPONSE-MSG IN L-PARAMETER
GO TO SUB-9000-EXIT

MOVE W-RECURSED-FORMAT-CHAR ( W-SUB-1 ) TO FAKER-RESULT IN L-PARAMETER ( W-SUB-2 : 1 )
ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1 W-SUB-2

ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1
GO TO SUB-2110-EXIT

MOVE W-SUB-1 TO W-SUB-1-SAVE
ADD 1 TO W-SUB-1
UNSTRING W-RECURSED-FORMAT DELIMITED W-FORMAT-END INTO W-FORMAT-ENTRY POINTER W-SUB-1

MOVE W-RECURSED-FORMAT ( W-SUB-1 : ) TO W-RECURSED-FORMAT-REST
MOVE W-SUB-1-SAVE TO W-SUB-1

SET FAKER-UNKNOWN-FUNCTION IN L-PARAMETER TO TRUE
STRING 'Unknown FAKCOMP function "' FAKER-PROVIDER-FUNCTION IN L-PARAMETER '"' DELIMITED SIZE INTO FAKER-RESPONSE-MSG IN L-PARAMETER
GO TO SUB-2000-EXIT

SET W-NOT-FIRST-CALL TO TRUE
MOVE FUNCTION WHEN-COMPILED TO W-COMPILED-DATE
DISPLAY 'FAKCOMP  compiled on ' W-COMPILED-DATE-YYYY '/' W-COMPILED-DATE-MM '/' W-COMPILED-DATE-DD ' at ' W-COMPILED-TIME-HH ':' W-COMPILED-TIME-MM ':' W-COMPILED-TIME-SS

PERFORM VARYING FC-DX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL FC-DX > FORMAT-COMPANY-CNT
ADD FORMAT-COMPANY-WEIGHT ( FC-DX ) TO FORMAT-COMPANY-WEIGHT-TOT
